POE/Wheel/Audio/Mad version 0.3
====================================

  This is *slightly* beta right now..  it has a fair
  amount of documentation but I can't guarantee that
  it looks very pretty.  It does work,  for me.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Audio::Mad (>= 0.5)
  Audio::OSS (>= 0.0501)
  
  libmad-0.14.x

